videos.headline: Kentucky's Ware comes up with INT
videos.description: Denzil Ware comes up with the heads up interception off the deflection

videos.headline: Vandy gets ball right back with fumble recovery
videos.description: LaDarius Wiley strips the ball and  Oren Burks comes up with the recovery to put Vanderbilt in good field position.

videos.headline: Webb finds the edge for 37-yard TD
videos.description: Ralph Webb bursts down the sideline for a 37-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky's King runs untouched for TD
videos.description: Sihiem King gets loose for a 22-yard touchdown to tie the game 7-7.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell spins for TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. spins off defenders for the 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Baity leaps up for INT
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur's pass is picked off by Derrick Baity who returns it 44 yards into Kentucky territory.

videos.headline: Coach Stoops discusses good team defense
videos.description: Kentucky head  coach Mark Stoops discusses good energy from his defense and his teams balanced rushing attack.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell takes direct snap in for TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr calls his own number and runs in for the 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Bowden catches pass and fumbles at goal line as ball bounces all over
videos.description: Lynn Bowden catches pass and fumbles as ball bounces near goal line but is recovered by Kent Walker Kentucky keeps position.

videos.headline: Kentucky's King finds a seam and runs in for the touchdown.
videos.description: Sihiem King finds a seam and runs in for the 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Bowden takes kickoff return for 93 yards
videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. returns kickoff 93-yards to set up Kentucky.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell runs in for his third TD today
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. gets third touchdown of the day on 6-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Vandy's  Shurmur finds Lipscomb for TD
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur connects with Kalija Lipscomb for 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell breaks down 44-21 win
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. discusses what drives his motivation as the Wildcats grab a big win.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Coach Stoops discusses his teams effort  in the win
videos.description: Head coach Mark Stoops discusses the win and effort from the running game
